::Trinity::

She meowed loudly, but then didn't hear a responce to her cries.  She got up 
and walked around the forest. She saw only dark trees and no one in sight.  
She wandered around for a while, deciding that since she was now lost, she'd 
need to find something to make her unlost. She wnet running in the direction 
of the sun and kept going.  All the while, she kept meowing and calling in 
hopes of one of her friends finding her.  She also hoped that one of the not 
so nice bots didn't find her.  So she kept running as fast as her little 
legs would go. "Meow!"
